Title: Domain events and the "Unit of Work" pattern
Description:
In this blog post, we will discuss the "Unit of Work" pattern and how it can be used to implement domain events in a DDD application.
For that, we will also discuss how we can leverage middleware to implement the "Unit of Work" pattern in a .NET application. A lot of things are going to happen in this blog post, so let's get started.
